1.	sudo yum install maven -y
1.	Internally the above command installs java.
2.	Verify maven installation
1.	mvn --version
3.	Create new java web application using maven
1.	mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=in.javahome -DartifactId=hr-api -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-webapp -DinteractiveMode=false
4.	cd hr-api
5.	mvn package
